{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"tool_586bb101-9784-4952-9ef8-3b354888d9d","tool_call":{"grepToolCall":{"args":{"pattern":"StoryPackageBundle|PackageBundle|collectReferenced","path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine","caseInsensitive":false,"multiline":false,"toolCallId":"tool_586bb101-9784-4952-9ef8-3b354888d9d","offset":0},"result":{"success":{"pattern":"StoryPackageBundle|PackageBundle|collectReferenced","path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine","outputMode":"content","workspaceResults":{"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine":{"content":{"matches":[{"file":"./.ai-workflow-v2-refine8/prompts/agent-1784715861772.log","matches":[{"lineNumber":30,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"tool_1bbac5e2-33fa-4ebc-8a6b-3a452bc50d9\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/细化修改8_需求.md\"},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"# Studio V2.0 · 细化修改 8 需求（编辑器与引擎 Content 契约总对齐）\\n\\n> **状态：** 已定稿，供实现与 Review / gbx 引用。  \\n> **性质：** 第三步 + 细化修改 7 之后的**总对齐批**：路径 B 全局角色库、包内卡生命周期、出口条件真写盘、资源真源、保存 validate 与定位、第三步 UX 债。目标：**作者仅靠 Studio 即可编出引擎 validate 可过的故事包**（仍不跑 Host 闭环）。  \\n> **人类讨论来源：** [原始需求讨论记录](../../../人类/原始需求讨论记录)（§896–916）；会话内「编辑器是否符合引擎特性」缺口评审结论。\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 1. 本轮定位\\n\\n### 1.1 要做什么\\n\\n```text\\n阶段 A · 引擎契约（路径 B）\\n  A1 story.conf.participants 可选/派生；collectReferencedAgentIds\\n  A2 validatePackage：按「包内被引用 agentId」校验；PARTICIPANT_* 降级\\n  A3 磁盘包迁移 + 需求 01/08 口径更新\\n\\n阶段 B · 包内卡生命周期（P0）\\n  B1 底栏/画布新建卡 → conf.cards[] + cards/<id>.s-card.json\\n  B2 画布删卡 → conf 移除 + 删磁盘 s-card（策略钉死）\\n  B3 entryCardId 可编；effect.critical roundtrip + 面板开关\\n\\n阶段 C · 出口条件与节拍（P0）\\n  C1 ExitCondition 编辑器 v1 [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":31,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"tool_f81c5cef-dd6f-40bd-8419-0ae10640843\",\"tool_call\":{\"readToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/细化修改8_执行索引.md\"},\"result\":{\"success\":{\"content\":\"---\\n# Studio V2.0 · 细化修改 8 执行索引（gbx / general-batch-exe）\\n# 用法：node .cursor/skills/general-batch-exe/bin/gbx.js --exFile <本文件> --workdir <仓库根> [--dry-run]\\n# 本轮目标：编辑器 Content 契约总对齐 — 路径 B + 卡生命周期 + ExitCondition + 资源真源 + validate 定位 + UX 债\\nbatch_size: 1\\nmax_rounds: 100\\nmax_fix_attempts: 5\\nmax_ineffective_fixes: 2\\nstop_on_fail: true\\ngroup: order\\n\\nverify_default:\\n  - npm run quality:engine\\n  - npm run quality:studio\\n\\nread_first:\\n  - AGENTS.md\\n  - .cursor/rules/codingRole.mdc\\n  - .cursor/rules/engine-boundaries.mdc\\n  - .cursor/rules/engine-code-quality.mdc\\n  - .cursor/rules/studio-boundaries.mdc\\n  - .cursor/rules/studio-v2-quality.mdc\\n  - .cursor/rules/testing-and-quality.mdc\\n  - .cursor/rules/docs-execution.mdc\\n  - docs/AI和人 [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":34,"content":"{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"subtype\":\"delta\",\"text\":\" `collectReferencedAgentIds`\",\"session_id\":\"bb8d042c-eb78-47ba-b62e-6d01943955de\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784715879997}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":41,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"started\",\"call_id\":\"tool_fbffacdb-42df-49b0-a65e-6bd43e7db8a\",\"tool_call\":{\"grepToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"pattern\":\"collectReferencedAgentIds|participants\",\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/packages/rpg-engine\",\"caseInsensitive\":false,\"multiline\":false,\"toolCallId\":\"tool_fbffacdb-42df-49b0-a65e-6bd43e7db8a\",\"offset\":0}},\"hookAdditionalContexts\":[],\"toolCallId\":\"tool_fbffacdb-42df-49b0-a65e-6bd43e7db8a\",\"startedAtMs\":\"1784715880079\"},\"model_call_id\":\"3a654a0f-ef17-4d6a-9b0a-d78b4ea717a4-2-ryop\",\"session_id\":\"bb8d042c-eb78-47ba-b62e-6d01943955de\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784715879999}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lin