{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"tool_b7c53d7c-41e6-4257-8e52-578c962e399","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md","offset":1,"limit":50},"result":{"success":{"content":"# 01. CallCard 数据模型\n\n本文定义 CallCard 体系的静态与运行时数据结构。实现时以 Zod（或等价）schema 为真源；本文为需求级描述。\n\n**存档口径**：`CallCardInstance` / `CallCardBoard` 挂在当前用户的 [PlayerProfile](./10-用户与存档.md) 下，不是全局单例。\n\n相关：[02-运行时协议](./02-运行时协议.md) · [11-角色与社交](./11-角色与社交.md) · [07-壳嵌入与导出契约](../技术设计文档/07-壳嵌入与导出契约.md)\n\n## 1. 两层对象\n\n| 层 | 类型 | 说明 |\n|----|------|------|\n| 静态 | `CallCardDefinition` | 写在 StoryPackage 里；可版本化、可编辑 |\n| 运行时 | `CallCardInstance` | 挂在某角色身上；带 status 与来源 |\n\n**禁止**把运行状态写回 Definition。同一张 Definition 可在不同 StoryInstance / 模拟中产生多个 Instance。\n\n## 2. CallCardDefinition\n\n```ts\ntype CardKind = \"free\" | \"story\" | \"system\"\ntype InteractionMode = \"realtime_dialogue\" | \"playback_only\" | \"hybrid\"\ntype EntryMode = \"inbound_user_dial\" | \"outbound_auto\" | \"either\"\n\ninterface CallCardDefinition {\n  cardId: string\n  cardKind: CardKind\n  title: string\n  ownerAgentId: string\n  entryMode: EntryMode\n  interactionMode: InteractionMode\n\n  context: CallCardContext\n  objectives: CallCardObjectives\n  toolPolicy: ToolPolicy\n  assets?: CardAssets\n\n  exits: CallCardExit[]\n}\n```\n\n### 2.1 cardKind\n\n| 值 | 含义 |\n|----|------|\n| `free` | 自由通话默认卡；每角色应有且仅有一份默认 FreeCallCard（可在角色库配置） |\n| `story` | 强约束剧情卡 |\n| `system` | 系统/媒介卡（过场播放、系统提示等） |\n\n### 2.2 entryMode","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":427,"fileSize":15758,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":50},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"tool_b7c53d7c-41e6-4257-8e52-578c962e399","startedAtMs":"1784715902723","completedAtMs":"1784715903071"},"model_call_id":"3a654a0f-ef17-4d6a-9b0a-d78b4ea717a4-8-jbrl","session_id":"bb8d042c-eb78-47ba-b62e-6d01943955de","timestamp_ms":1784715902987}
